h2. *Update* {{2026-01-30}}

*Root cause:*  {color:#ff5630}*Data synchronization mechanism issue of iotAgent with XMS*{color}
*Verified version:* {color:#ff991f}*04.03.00.master-1427*{color}

When Duvel was not connected to XMS, iotAgent did not work. I tested turning *Energy saver* on or off, modifying the *Energy save mode* and *Timeout(min)*, and then after about 3 seconds, I immediately unplugged the power and restarted the Duvel. 

{color:#006644}*The values were correctly displayed on the settings page,*{color} because the ticket

[https://barco-nv.atlassian.net/browse/CS0666-6733|https://barco-nv.atlassian.net/browse/CS0666-6733|smart-link]   fix this issue, so the Duvel wasn’t connected to XMS was ruled out as an interference.



